  {"word":"public","level":"middle","meaning":"공공의, 대중","pronunciation":"/ˈpʌblɪk/","parts":[{"type":"root","text":"publ","meaning":"사람 (people)"},{"type":"suffix","text":"-ic","meaning":"형용사형"}],"story":"모든 '사람(publ)'들을 위한 → 공공의.","example":{"en":"Public transportation.","ko":"대중교통."}},
